ce:section.ce:para:
In light of the findings in this paper, future research can investigate these topics, among others:

                           •

The quantification of footprints for further regions by applying this method;


                           •

The calculation of impacts by multiplying the footprints (inventory of inputs and outputs) by impact factors;


                           •

The appropriate prioritization of topics for industries, by using footprints and other criteria;


                           •

The quantification of footprints at the company level, by further breaking down industry footprints or by using a company's own environmental data.
